--Create Invoice--
SupplierServiceImpl.java method getSupplierERPIds
It fetches data from SIM. How it calls web services.

newSimUrl = http://192.168.2.70:10280/sim/api_v1/suppliersearchws.do
simTenantId = 9010062a-f20c-4ad0-af0e-e3384c234f21

// SupplierSearchConstants.SEARCH_IN_DBA_IDS = 6
queryCriteria.addCondition(SupplierSearchConstants.SEARCH_IN_DBA_IDS , {967494,});
converted above queryCriteria to following JSON
{
  "startIndex": -1,
  "recordsPerPage": -1,
  "sortColumnName": -1,
  "isAscending": true,
  "reqTotalResultCount": false,
  "escapeCharacter": "\u0000",
  "queryConditions": [
    {
      "columnName": 6,
      "columnValue": [
        "967494"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "tmsClientId": "9010062a-f20c-4ad0-af0e-e3384c234f21"
}
then wrote this JSON to Connection's outputStream
Took Connection's inputstream in a bufferedReader
bufferedReader = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(conn.getInputStream()));
while ((output = bufferedReader.readLine()) != null)
{
